OL,3,CCapture IT scandal: Postmasters could
OL,4,Creceive #300,000 under new redress
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FThe first compensation scheme for
OL,8,Fvictims of the Post Office Capture
OL,9,Fscandal has been launched.
OL,11,FCapture, which was a precursor to the
OL,12,Finfamous Horizon system, led to a
OL,13,Fnumber of sub-postmasters being
OL,14,Faccused of "accounting malpractice,"
OL,15,Fwith some having their contracts
OL,16,Fterminated.
OL,18,FSome resigned, while others were
OL,19,Fprosecuted or had to pay money back.
