OL,3,CCapture IT scandal: Postmasters could
OL,4,Creceive #300,000 under new redress
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FEarlier this year, in a move to "right
OL,8,Fthe wrongs of the past," the
OL,9,Fgovernment announced the new redress
OL,10,Fscheme for those affected by the
OL,11,Ffaults of Capture between 1992 and
OL,12,F2000.
OL,14,FEligible postmasters will receive
OL,15,Fimmediate preliminary payments of
OL,16,F#10,000, with an independent panel
OL,17,Fthen assessing final awards through a
OL,18,Fbanding model ranging from #10,000 to
OL,19,F#300,000.
