OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FIn exceptional cases, awards may
OL,8,Fexceed the upper limit.
OL,10,FThe scheme launches with an initial
OL,11,Fphase for 150 claimants to ensure the
OL,12,Fprocess is fair and accessible before
OL,13,Fwider implementation.
OL,15,FIt comes after the government accepted
OL,16,Ffindings from an independent
OL,17,Finvestigation by Kroll Associates,
OL,18,Fwhich concluded there was a reasonable
OL,19,Flikelihood that Capture created
OL,20,Ffinancial shortfalls for postmasters.
